<br>
So if I am leading a raid to Karnors and I want to reserve every single plague mite which drops, that is my perrogative.  I must be certain to make sure everyone knows that this is my intention though.  <br>
<br>
Of course, this also means that those who think about attending really ought to agree with the raid's rules before signing up.  Otherwise they should not attend.  And if they are joining a raid spontaneously where there might be a drop for their epic, it would be in their best interest to ask about the drop and how it would be distributed before they go too far with the raid.<br>
<br>
